{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS01.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Your favourite Cry Babies characters are ready to play! <br><br>The Big Game is a friendly and fun adventure perfect for young players. Join Lady, Coney, Dreamy and friends in an all-new adventure as they take part in an exciting multi-stage tournament to win the fabled Golden Pacifier! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Animated_Series.png?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Players can meet and play as 15 popular Cry Babies characters, and explore familiar locations from Baby Bottle Valley to Fantasy Mountain, Tutti Frutti Bay, Icy World and finally to a new planet, Planet Tear! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS10.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Minigames.png?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Take part in lots of fun activities to progress, including hide and seek, mazes, puzzles, dancing, taking photos and even having a bath!  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS11.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Play_Together.png?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Cry Babies love their friends, so just use a second controller and two players can cooperate for double the fun! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS03.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Customise.png?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Collect pink stars by exploring then spend them on new clothes and outfits for your favourite characters! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS05.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Fully_Animated.png?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>All story scenes are animated and voiced just like the TV series, so players will feel they\u2019re taking part in a whole new interactive episode! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS18.jpg?t=1738065375\" /><br><br>Each victory takes them to a new world from their popular animated series. From Baby Bottle Valley to Fantasy Mountain, Tutti Frutti Bay, Icy World and finally to a new planet, Planet Tear! Along the way they\u2019ll play hide and seek, dance, dress up, explore mazes and solve puzzles. They can even stop to take a bath! <br><br>Despite the glittering prize, the Cry Babies always work together to help each other succeed!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458250/extras/Cry-Babies-SS22.jpg?t=1738065375\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Platinum pacifier","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2458250/8abe1d9ad9ef554fff3b3d2d9de2b3d91abcb467.jpg"},{"name":"Bottle Valley","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2458250/be665457de7cb7a1d4f106e518c847e477578b98.jpg"},{"name":"Fantasy Mountain","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2458250/aa29a033047fc7a5b3e994a835f7b7092fa66361.jpg"},{"name":"TuttiFrutti Bay","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2458250/f9bc669162242834fe5ca94fc364d5b3a9947d3b.jpg